We carry out the simulations for $\kappa_1=\kappa_2=0$ for which there is no work production according to Eq.~(\ref{work_nc}). Only heat is produced but gradually ceases as the system approaches the steady state. Fig.~\ref{fig1} confirms the expectation. We confirm the steady state to be in equilibrium by observing the Boltzmann distribution proportional to $e^{-\beta k(x^2+y^2)/2}$ in two dimensions.

